- `server/etcdmain/config.go` defines ProxyDialTimeoutMs configuration (default 1000ms) as a command-line flag via "--proxy-dial-timeout"
- `server/etcdmain/etcd.go` converts ProxyDialTimeoutMs to time.Duration and passes it to proxy transport creation
- `server/etcdmain/grpc_proxy.go` creates etcd client configurations with DialTimeout set to 5 seconds for both proxy client connections and standard client configurations
- `pkg/proxy/server.go` defines a ServerConfig struct with DialTimeout field for proxy server configuration

